<a href="#recipe-video" data-recipe="5561" style="color: #000000;" class="wprm-recipe-jump-video wprm-recipe-link wprm-jump-to-video-shortcode wprm-block-text-normal wprm-jump-smooth-scroll" data-smooth-scroll="0"><span class="wprm-recipe-icon wprm-recipe-jump-video-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewbox="0 0 24 24"><g class="nc-icon-wrapper" fill="#000000"><path fill="#000000" d="M22,8H2C1.448,8,1,8.447,1,9v14c0,0.553,0.448,1,1,1h20c0.552,0,1-0.447,1-1V9C23,8.447,22.552,8,22,8z M9,20v-8l7,4L9,20z"></path> <rect data-color="color-2" x="0.001" y="2.111" transform="matrix(0.9798 -0.1999 0.1999 0.9798 -0.4028 2.2323)" width="21.701" height="2"></rect></g></svg></span> Jump to Video</a></div><div class="dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden" style="display: none;"><img data-perfmatters-preload width="600" height="900" src="https://theunlikelybaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Easy-Cherry-Cake-Recipe-Pinterest.jpg" data-pin-title="Easy Cherry Cake Recipe from Scratch" data-pin-description="This easy cherry cake recipe is so easy to make and so delicious you’d want to bake it all summer long. Dense but soft, not too sweet, bursting with wonderful cherry flavour." alt="Easy Cherry Cake Recipe from Scratch" class="dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden-inner  dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden-single" loading="lazy" fetchpriority="high"></div>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">This <strong>easy cherry cake recipe </strong>is so easy to make and so delicious you&rsquo;d want to bake it all summer long. Dense but soft, not too sweet, bursting with wonderful cherry flavour.</span></p>



<p class="p1"><span class="s1">(Take advantage of cherry season and make some </span><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="https://theunlikelybaker.com/mini-cherry-galette/">mini cherry galettes</a></span></strong><span class="s1">. Buttery, flaky crust. Plump, juicy, sweet cherries. It&rsquo;s your favourite summer pie without all the work. This </span><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="https://theunlikelybaker.com/chocolate-cherry-bundt-cake-video-recipe/">chocolate cherry bundt cake</a></span></strong><span class="s1"> is easy to make and looks stunning!)</span></p>


<div class="wp-block-image">
<figure class="aligncenter size-full"><img decoding="async" width="680" height="900" src="https://theunlikelybaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Easy-Cherry-Cake-Recipe-1.jpg" alt="Easy Cherry Cake Recipe from Scratch" data-skip-lazy class="wp-image-5552" srcset="https://theunlikelybaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Easy-Cherry-Cake-Recipe-1.jpg 680w, https://theunlikelybaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Easy-Cherry-Cake-Recipe-1-227x300.jpg 227w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" data-pin-media="https://theunlikelybaker.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Easy-Cherry-Cake-Recipe-1.jpg"></figure></div>

<div class="lwptoc lwptoc-baseItems lwptoc-dark lwptoc-notInherit" data-smooth-scroll="1" data-smooth-scroll-offset="80"><div class="lwptoc_i">    <div class="lwptoc_header">
