                <span class="lwptoc_item_label">Other cake recipes that are easy to make from scratch</span>
    </a>
    </div><div class="lwptoc_item">    <a href="#Easy_Cherry_Cake_Recipe_from_Scratch">
                <span class="lwptoc_item_label">Easy Cherry Cake Recipe from Scratch</span>
    </a>
